---
title: Perfect Penne Pasta with Chicken Sausage and Kale
description: When we say this recipe is perfect, we really mean it. It’s got all the gooey deliciousness of lasagna with none of the hassle or tedious layering. Featuring tender kale, hearty chicken sausage, a good sprinkle of cheese, and penne cooked until it’s just al dente, it’s a pasta-lover’s fantasy.
